===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The act of [[merge|merging]].
# {{law}} An absorption of one [[estate]], or one [[contract]], into another, both being held by the same person.
# {{economics}} The legal union of two or more [[corporation]]s into a single entity, [[asset]]s and [[liability|liabilities]] being assumed by the buying firm.

